                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/4895" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OM-0206</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8397 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">高效至精，降损求益—龙骧巴士精益管理之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Efficient to precise, loss reduction and seeking profit——Lean management process of Long Xiang Bus</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">匡茂华，彭莞莎，刘洪伟</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">湘潭大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">湖南龙骧巴士责任有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">交通运输业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">生产运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">龙骧巴士；精益管理；预算维修；JIT准时化</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">LongXiang&#160;Bus; Lean&#160;management;Budget&#160;maintenance， JIT Just In Time</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">公交企业作为城市的动脉，是一个城市发展的重要载体。城市的发展离不开交通系统高效的运行，而交通系统的高效运行需要以公交企业先进的管理方式为前提。本案例以龙骧巴士为研究对象，对其运营管理、维修制度等进行分析,了解从2006年引入精益管理思想到逐步实践落地，企业运营效率由低向高转变的过程。旨在引导学生学习准时化、全面生产维修等管理相关工具在交通服务等行业的灵活应用，对提高服务型企业的管理效率和企业利润具有重要现实意义。
</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all"> As the artery of the city, public transportation enterprise is an essential carrier of  urban development.The&#160;development&#160;of&#160;a city&#160;is&#160;inseparable&#160;from&#160;the&#160;efficient&#160;operation&#160;of&#160;the&#160;transportation&#160;system,&#160;which&#160;requires&#160;the&#160;advanced&#160;management&#160;of&#160;public&#160;transportation&#160;enterprises&#160;as&#160;the&#160;premise.&#160;This&#160;case&#160;takes&#160;Longxiang&#160;Bus&#160;as&#160;the&#160;object&#160;of&#160;study.&#160;It&#160;analyzes&#160;its&#160;operation&#160;management&#160;and&#160;maintenance&#160;system&#160;to&#160;understand&#160;the&#160;process&#160;of&#160;enterprise&#160;operation&#160;efficiency&#160;changing&#160;from&#160;low&#160;to&#160;high&#160;from&#160;lean&#160;management&#160;thought&#160;introduced&#160;in&#160;2006&#160;to&#160;practice&#160;and&#160;implementation&#160;step&#160;by&#160;step.&#160;It&#160;aims&#160;to&#160;guide&#160;students&#160;to&#160;learn&#160;the&#160;flexible&#160;application&#160;of&#160;management&#160;tools&#160;such&#160;as&#160;just-in-time,&#160;comprehensive&#160;production&#160;and&#160;maintenance&#160;in&#160;the&#160;transportation&#160;service&#160;industry,&#160;which&#160;is&#160;of&#160;great&#160;practical&#160;significance&#160;to&#160;improve&#160;service oriented&#160;enterprises&#39;&#160;management&#160;efficiency and&#160;profit.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《生产运作管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">质量成本、质量的经济性、质量成本分析与报告、质量改进</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
